<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمُنْكَرُ وَالْمَعْرُوفُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٨٣ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْمُنْكَرُ»</span>: الَّذِي رَوَى غَيْرُ الثِّقَهْ … مُخَالِفاً؛ فِي <span style="color:#6c6c00">«نُخْبَةٍ»</span> قَدْ حَقَّقَهْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٨٤ - قَابَلَهُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْمَعْرُوفُ»</span>، وَالَّذِي رَأَى … تَرَادُفَ الْمُنْكَرِ وَالشَّاذِ نَأَى<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
